pageContext.claim: “We've achieved more in this month alone than almost any President has achieved in eight years in office, if you think about it -- if you think what we've done.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump's biggest accomplishment in the last month was passage of the USMCA trade deal, which revises key parts of NAFTA. It's absurd to claim this revision of an existing trade deal exceeds what previous presidents have done over the course of their full terms.
